<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tidak ada pengguna atau ditolak</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.unpkg.com/bulma@0.9.3/css/bulma.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.unpkg.com/bulma@0.9.3/css/bulma.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo_tix_icon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <style>
        ::-webkit-scrollbar{
            background-color: #ffffff;
            width: 3px;
            height: 3px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{
            background-color: #001A3A;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar is-dark" role="navigation" aria-label="main navigation" style="background-color: #001A3A;">
            <div class="navbar-start">
                <img src="/images/logo_tix_png.png" class="navbar-brand" alt="" width="50">
                <a role="button" class="navbar-burger burger" aria-label="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-target="navbarBasicExample">
                    <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </a>
                  <div class="navbar-menu">
                    <div class="navbar-start">
                      <a href="/" class="navbar-item">Tix Online</a>
                      <a href="#" class="navbar-item">Carrers</a>
                      <% if (user.isAdmin) { %> 
                        <a href="/admin/product" class="navbar-item">Product Dashboard</a>
                      <% } %>
                    </div>
                  </div>
            </div>

            <div class="navbar-menu">
                <div class="navbar-end">
                    <div class="navbar-item">
                        <div class="mx-3">
                            <%= user.email %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="buttons">
                            <%- (!user?'<a href="/user/login" class="button is-light">Login</a>':'<a href="/user/logout" class="button is-light">Logout</a>') %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div id="app" class="container is-max-desktop">
        <div class="columns mt-5">
            <div class="column is-8 is-offset-2">
                <div class="content is-medium">
                    <h1 class="title">Forbidden</h1>
                    <p>Ops, Anda tidak memiliki hak akses pada halaman tersebut. Harap hubungi administrator untuk informasi lebih lanjut.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>